result.reason: mRemoteNG correctly sets RedirectPrinters=true on the MSTSC ActiveX control (AdvancedSettings2); inconsistent printer counts across different servers indicate a limitation of the RDP ActiveX control itself, not mRemoteNG code
result.approach: No actionable fix — the RedirectPrinters boolean is correctly passed to the ActiveX control; mstsc.exe uses its own internal RDP stack (not the ActiveX control) which handles printer enumeration differently
